==Russian==
===Etymology===
From deliberately misspelled '''[[в]] [[топка|топку]]''', literally ''into [[furnace]]''. 
===Idiom===
'''фтопку!''' (ftópku) 
#(''as [[imperative]]'') [[Burn]] it! [[Delete]] it!
===Usage note===
Popular Internet slang expression. Belongs to the so called [[:w:Padonki|Padonki]]'s slang ([[жаргон]] [[падонки|падонков]]). Presumably originated as a cynical allusion to [[crematories]] of the Nazi extermination camps.

